/10/31/canon-pulling-the-eos-1d-mark-iii-from-shelves/#comments</comments><description><![CDATA[<p>Filed under: <a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/category/digitalcameras/" rel="tag">數位相機</a></p><div align="center"><a href="http://www.robgalbraith.com/bins/multi_page.asp?cid=7-8740-9068-9134"><img vspace="4" hspace="4" border="0" src="http://www.blogsmithmedia.com/www.engadget.com/media/2007/10/2308_canon_uk_letter_highlighted-440.jpg" alt="" /></a><br /></div>
Canon 的 EOS-1D Mark III 前陣子<a href="http://www.engadget.com/2007/10/19/canon-planning-fix-for-eos-1d-mark-iii-autofocus-issue/">被懷疑有自動對焦的問題</a>。雖然官方到現在都沒還有一個說法，但許多零售商都收到了這封看起來來自官方的信函，上頭明確的寫著 Canon 了解自動對焦的問題確實存在，但只影響極少數的產品。可是接下來的兩段就有點自相矛盾了：一方面寫著「為了確保顧客滿意度不受影響，Canon 決定停止 EOS-1D Mark III 的供貨。同時，我們希望能回收您手中所有的 EOS-1D Mark III 存貨。」，但另一方面卻又說「對於有問題的售出產品，我們正確尋求解決方案... Canon 接受維修，但將不提供交換或回收。」<br /><br />Canon 啊 Canon，既然顧客滿意度這麼重要，那你就有責任要讓每個售出的產品都是完美的，何況這還是旗艦機 EOS-1D Mark III？對於全面回收的決定我們給你拍拍手，但已經花了大錢買下去的人，也應該要得到同等的照顧才是吧？<br /><br />[<a href="http://www.engadget.com/2007/10/30/canon-pulling-the-eos-1d-mark-iii-from-shelves/">原文連結</a>]<h6 style="clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;"></h6><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 2px; margin: 0; font-size: x-small;"></td><td style="text-align: right; vertical-align: top; padding: 2px; margin: 0; font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/canon-pulling-the-eos-1d-mark-iii-from-shelves/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to this entry">永久連結</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/forward/1025943/" title="Send this entry to a friend via email">轉寄</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/canon-pulling-the-eos-1d-mark-iii-from-shelves/#comments" title="View reader comments on this entry">發表回應</a></td></tr></table>]]></description><category>Canon</category><category>Eos 1D Mark III</category><category>Eos1dMarkIii</category><dc:creator>Andy Yang</dc:creator><dc:date>2007-10-31T02:00:00+00:00</dc:date></item><item><title>免費！英國3 Skypephone</title><link>http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/3-skypephone-set-free-in-the-uk/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/3-skypephone-set-free-in-the-uk/</guid><comments>http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/3-skypephone-set-free-in-the-uk/#comments</comments><description><![CDATA[<p>Filed under: <a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/category/mobilephones/" rel="tag">手機</a>, <a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/category/wireless/" rel="tag">無線相關</a></p><br />
<div id="1025451" class="post"><a href="http://right%20on%20schedule,%20you%27re%20looking%20at%20the%20just%20announced%20co-branded%20skype%20phone:20/;%20Australia,%20Austria,%20Denmark,%20Hong%20Kong,%20Italy,%20Ireland,%20Macau%20and%20Sweden%20sometime%20later%20in%20the%20year.%20Wanna%20see%20it%20in%20a%20video?%20Sure%20you%20do,%20locked-and-loaded%20right%20after%20the%20break." minmax_bound="true"><img vspace="4" hspace="4" border="1" alt="" src="http://www.blogsmithmedia.com/www.engadget.com/media/2007/10/3_skypephone_440.jpg" minmax_bound="true" /></a></div>
<br />鏘鏘，你們現在看到的這款就是<a href="http://www.engadget.com/2007/10/26/3skypephone-launching-november-2nd/">即將上市</a>的貼牌Skype手機：3 Skypephone（不是3台Skypephone喔）。太好啦，全世界人民都歡呼雀躍準備迎接Skype手機的到來吧！不管怎麼說，這是全球第一款內嵌原生Skype功能的手機，將對傳統的電信業務產生不可估量的巨大衝擊。<br /><br />根據3公司（香港和記黃埔負責3G業務的子公司）的規劃，只要你簽訂協定成為3公司的合約用戶，或者每月交少少的10英鎊（約新台幣650元）月租，與其他Skype用戶之間產生的Skype VoIP通話以及簡訊統統免費。<br /><br />這只零售價49英鎊（約新台幣3,200元）的3G手機內建200萬像素攝影鏡頭，支援microSD記憶卡擴展，3 Skypephone 將於本周5將在英國上市。今年年內晚些時候登陸澳洲、奧地利、丹麥、香港、義大利、愛爾蘭、澳門及瑞典等國家/地區。想看實機操作視訊？麻煩你翻牆吧～<br /><br />[整理編譯自 <a href="http://www.t3.co.uk/news/247/communications/mobile_phone/3s_skype_phone_official">T3</a>]<br /><br />[撰文：rex]<br /><h6 style="clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;"></h6><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 2px; margin: 0; font-size: x-small;"></td><td style="text-align: right; vertical-align: top; padding: 2px; margin: 0; font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/3-skypephone-set-free-in-the-uk/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to this entry">永久連結</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/forward/1025946/" title="Send this entry to a friend via email">轉寄</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/31/3-skypephone-set-free-in-the-uk/#comments" title="View reader comments on this entry">發表回應</a></td></tr></table>]]></description><category>skype</category><dc:creator>Atticus Wu</dc:creator><dc:date>2007-10-31T00:01:00+00:00</dc:date></item><item><title>Dell XPS ONE裸機登場</title><link>http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/30/dells-xps-one-gets-undressed-and-naughty/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/30/dells-xps-one-gets-undressed-and-naughty/</guid><comments>http://chinese.engadget.com/2007/10/30/dells-xps-one-gets-undressed-and-naughty/#comments</comments><description><![CDATA[<p>Filed under: <a href="http://chinese.engadget.com/cate